title: Ep. #69 | Solo Artists: Crush, Somi, LeeHi
description:
Today's episode of K-Pop Daebak is all about solo artists! Eric sits down to review 'OHIO' by Crush, 'What You Waiting For' by Somi, and '홀로 (HOLO)' by Lee Hi.


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
